e=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xuv1665702843889.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xuv1665702843889.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xuv1665702843889.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xuv1665702843889\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Supported Image Formats\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Uniface provides a wide range of filters that transparently support many image formats. Loading an image that has been stored in a supported format causes it to appear, whatever the runtime graphical environment.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xuv1665702843889__p_d11849e1_d11850e1_d11851e1\">The image filters only work with bitmap-oriented image formats. Vector-oriented mark-up languages such as PostScript and HP-GL are not supported.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xuv1665702843889__p_d11852e1_d11853e1_d11854e1\">The image filters recognize the format of the image to be loaded from the file extension, or, if that is not available, the header information of the image data.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xuv1665702843889__p_d11855e1_d11856e1_d11857e1\">The image filters in Uniface only work in one direction. They can load any of the supported image formats and convert it to a proprietary format that can be displayed on all platforms. They cannot convert one format to another, or export from the Uniface format to another format.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"xuv1665702843889__table_d1247e1_d1248e1_d1249e1_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"xuv1665702843889__table_d1247e1_d1248e1_d1249e1_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"xuv1665702843889__table_d1247e1_d1248e1_d1249e1\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">Column<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-filter\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-filter\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\"><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Format-0-0\" id=\"topic-Format-0-0\" name=\"topic-Format-0-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Format-0-0\">Format</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Description-1-0\" id=\"topic-Description-1-0\" name=\"topic-Description-1-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Description-1-0\">Description</label></div></div><div class=\"searchAllTable\"><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-all-smart-table\">Filter results...</label><input aria-label=\"Filter results in the table\" class=\"zDocsInputField\" id=\"search-all-smart-table\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/><button aria-label=\"Submit\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldSearch\" type=\"submit\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-search\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-search\"></use></svg></button><div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"sr-only\">22 rows found</div></div><div><button aria-label=\"Export table to a file\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageTableExportButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-v\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-v\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicPageTableExportMenu\"><button aria-label=\"Export to Excel\" class=\"dropdown-item\" type=\"button\">Export to Excel</button><button aria-label=\"Export to CSV\" class=\"dropdown-item\" type=\"button\">Export to CSV</button></div></div></div><div class=\"dataTables_scroll\" data-testid=\"sticky-header-table\"><div class=\"dataTables_scrollHead\" style=\"overflow: hidden; positio